In this video, I take a journey back to the Xbox 360 era as we approach the final days of its digital store. I explore some of the best deals and hidden gems still available, while also testing how well the system holds up in 2024. Along the way, I uncover some surprising insights about backwards compatibility and the importance of preserving these classic games.
